      "span_text": "Additional benefits of using technology versus paper and pen include ease of capturing key information and ease of reporting outcomes.  25 eScreening provides an opportunity for patients in a primary care setting to participate in their care in an active way by reporting key information about how they are doing using psychometrically tested instruments."
